#Cosmos Docks

Cosmos Docks is a custom 9-key macropad designed from scratch for Hack Club Stardance. It includes a custom PCB, a fully 3D-printable case, one rotary encoder, an OLED display, and SK6812MINI-E addressable RGB LEDs.

The design is built around the Seeed XIAO RP2040 and uses QMK firmware.

##Features
9 MX-style mechanical switches
1 EC11 rotary encoder
0.91 inch 128×32 I2C OLED display
13 SK6812MINI-E addressable RGB LEDs
Seeed XIAO RP2040 microcontroller
Custom 2-layer PCB designed in KiCad
Fully 3D-printable top and bottom case
QMK firmware with OLED, encoder, and RGB Matrix support
M3 screws and heat-set inserts for case assembly

